  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Zentabia</span> Fluid is a pote=
nt
  healing fluid made from the rare <span class=3DSpellE>Zentabia</span> flo=
wer.
  These flowers occasionally grow in sheltered crevices on Volcanic worlds.
  Their petals are <span class=3DSpellE>colored</span> a brilliant green. T=
hey
  thrive in very hot environments.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Zentabia</span> fluid <span lan=
g=3DEN-GB
  style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>can heal nearly any wo=
und or
  disease. It can even repair damaged limbs or organs. Any colony supplied =
with
  Zentabia fluid thus receives a 30% development bonus, over and above any
  other bonus. Once discovered, every effort should be made to control the =
trade
  of this highly valuable resource.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Occurrence: extremely rare</p>
